# ==========================================
# 1. 编译产物和构建目录 (重点清理)
# ==========================================
# 忽略所有 cmake 生成的构建目录
cmake-build-*/
build/
out/
bin/

# 忽略具体的目标文件
*.exe
*.obj
*.o
*.a
*.lib
*.so
*.dll
*.dylib

# ==========================================
# 2. 外部库例外规则 (最关键)
# ==========================================
# 先允许 Git 进入 external 目录（防止被上面的 bin/ 或 *.dll 误杀）
!external/
# 允许 external 目录下的二进制文件被提交
!external/**/*.dll
!external/**/*.so
!external/**/*.dylib
!external/**/bin/

# ==========================================
# 3. IDE 与 环境文件
# ==========================================
.idea/
.vscode/
*.iml
*.user
*.suo
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
cmake_install.cmake
Makefile
build.ninja
rules.ninja

# ==========================================
# 4. 临时与日志
# ==========================================
*.log
*.swp
*.tmp
*.bak